dith on Akhlaq: O Allah, make my character excellent","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 18, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, You have made my creation beautiful, thus make my character beautiful.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 959 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Arna'ut \u00a0\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22894,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/05\/09\/abu-darda-dua-akhlaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":22426,"position":1},"title":"Abu Darda on Akhlaq: Supplicating all night for good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Darda reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with them both, stood praying and weeping, saying, \u201cO Allah, you have made my form excellent, so make my character excellent.\u201d He continued until the morning and I said, \u201cO Abu Darda, you did not supplicate for anything but good character!\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24976,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/08\/kab-moses-merciful-creation\/","url_meta":{"origin":22426,"position":2},"title":"Ka\u2019b on Mercy: Blessed are those who are merciful to creation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b reported: Allah Almighty said to Moses, upon him be peace, \u201cO Moses, be soft in nature, for the most abhorred creation to me is one within whom is arrogance, in whose tongue is sharpness, and in whose heart is hardness. The most beloved character traits to me are mercy,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24835,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/21\/allah-jamil-yuhibbu-jamal\/","url_meta":{"origin":22426,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Beauty: Allah is beautiful, loves beautiful character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah is beautiful and He loves beauty. He loves the loftiest of affairs and disapproves of pettiness.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 6906 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":484,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/02\/01\/prophet-sent-husn-akhlaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":22426,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Character: The Prophet was sent to perfect good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI have been sent to perfect good character.\u201d Source: al-Muwat\u0323t\u0323a' 1614 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u00a0Ibn Abdul Barr \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0628\u064f\u0639\u0650\u062b\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0644\u0650\u0623\u064f\u062a\u064e\u0645\u0650\u0651\u0645\u064e \u062d\u064f\u0633\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u062e\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0642\u0650 1614 \u0645\u0648\u0637\u0623 \u0645\u0627\u0644\u0643 \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0627\u0645\u0639 \u0628\u0627\u0628\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32100,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/achieve-greatness-husn-khuluq\/","url_meta":{"origin":22426,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Khuluq: Allah lets him achieve greatness by good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":fa